snippet.title: (Long Play) Time Bokan Series: Bokan Desuyo [PS1] 5,475,680
snippet.description:
Time Bokan Series: Bokan Desuyo (タイムボカンシリーズ：ぼかんですよ) , (Banpresto, 1998) on the Playstation 1, default game, long play, all cut scenes and full ending included.  Really fun game, great bosses, graphics, music, sounds... Next up I'll try to tackle the "Hard" level with 2 extra stages. I was hoping for a no-damage run but screwed up this run a few times, even bicycled out but rebounded.




#TimeBokan #BokanDesuyo #PS1
